          "$24$",
          "$0$",
          "$4$",
          "$16$"
        ],
        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "$f(-2) = 3(-2)^2 - 5(-2) + 2 = 3(4) + 10 + 2 = 12 + 10 + 2 = 24$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Given $f(x) = 2x + 1$ and $g(x) = x - 5$, find $(f + g)(x)$.",
        "options": [
          "$3x - 4$",
          "$3x + 6$",
          "$2x - 4$",
          "$x + 6$"
        ],
        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "$(f + g)(x) = (2x + 1) + (x - 5) = 3x - 4$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "If $f(x) = x^2$ and $g(x) = \sqrt{x}$, what is the domain of $(f/g)(x)$?",
